    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>This is how it is done using the fluent interface of the <a href=\"http://www.op4j.org\" rel=\"nofollow\">op4j</a> Java library (1.1. was released Dec '10) :-</p>\n\n<pre><code>List&lt;String&gt; names = Op.onListFor(\"Ryan\", \"Julie\", \"Bob\").get();\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>It's a very cool library that saves you a tonne of time.</p>\n"
  }, {
    "owner" : {
      "account_id" : 3634475,
